Title: Ghosts of War
Cast: Brenton Thwaites, Theo Rossi, Skylar Astin, Kyle Gallner, Alan Ritchson, Billy Zane, Shaun Toub
Description: Five, battle-worn Allied soldiers guarding a chateau previously occupied by Nazis start experiencing unexplained and terrifying supernatural horrors.

Title: The Forgotten
Cast: Clem Tibber, Elarica Johnson, James Doherty, Shaun Dingwall, Lyndsey Marshal
Description: After a teenager goes to live with his father in abandoned public housing, he hears strange noises and decides to investigate with his new friend.
